8. Nf3{ This was the classical approach. It is less critical than  Bb5 + but also has some danger if we are not ready. It is usually the outcome of the 4 pawns attack against the King's Indian, so all of you who want to switch from the King's Indian to some Benoni might have special interest here. }
8. O-O
