9. Nbd7{ I prefer this move as only  O-O + Nd2  (doesn't matter the move order) is the way to go for White. }( { Against }9...Re8 { we need to check  Nd2  and  e5 . Both are fine for Black, but this is simpler. } )
10. e5{ This is the main reason why I choose this move order. This tempting move is just plain bad. }
