13. Rxe4{ White has a couple other tries. }( 13.Qa4 { is countered by }13...Nd7! { and we will recover the piece later on with  Nb6 - axb5 . } )( 13.Ng5 { is a really creative idea, but just going back with }13...Nf6 { is more than enough, as the knight on  g5  would be somewhat out of place. } )
13. Rxe4
