12. e4{ Recently I've been testing this repertoire in the Aimchess-Rapid-Play-In and my opponent played my idea! I said White plays  e2 - e3 , as playing  e4  in one go is not possible. But the simple concept of looking to play  e3 - e4  whenever possible makes a lot of sense and was a novelty when I published my course. }
