14. dxe5{ We make room for the knight on  d6  and get an amazing blockade. We would love to have our queenside more flexible (which can be obtained without including ... a6 ,  a4 , BUT this would also imply knowing 8.  Qa4 + variation.) but in general, this is very safe. White has a very good and safe pawn structure but very few dynamic options, so we are in command of creating stuff. }
