12. Bf5{ Playing  h6 - g5  helps us to develop our  c8 -bishop FINALLY. Over 16 games, only a couple of wins with White and precisely correspondence games. Another couple were blitz games. BUT, like a very big BUT with red neon and flashy lights, White lost 10 games.     It's funny to point out that even Srinath Narayanan won with black, who's basically the one recommending it for White in his course 🙂. I mean I definitely lost games with lines I recommend and vice versa, chess is far richer than just the openings, but I'll let that sink in 😜.      Now after the friendly banter is over (please keep checking his nice ideas that helped many young stars from India to be +2600), paying attention to chess, White's only serious try to justify his plan is  h2 - h4 . ... Nbd7  or ... Ne4  would be our next moves otherwise, and  Nd2  is out of the equation still thanks to ... Ng4 . }
