8. Bg4{ I like this creative way to tease our opponent. }( 8...e4 { would be fine as well, I'd say. We have a funny threat in ... Qb6 ! } )
9. h3
9. Qb6{ That's the trick! The 'obvious move' (9. h3 ) fails. }
10. hxg4
10. Bxf2+
11. Kd2
11. Nc6{ Development is always the solution! }
12. dxc6{ Again, the most tempting move loses. }
